the best theory I’ve seen so far was that

00:01:24.850 --> 00:01:28.990
she’s their love child and was raised in
the doctrine of the red lotus.

00:01:28.990 --> 00:01:34.670
The timelines are a little fuzzy but here’s
what we know.

00:01:34.670 --> 00:01:39.990
The Red Lotus was formed after the 100 year
war by Xai Bau after he got pissed that they

00:01:39.990 --> 00:01:44.560
White Lotus was turned into what he saw as
glorified servants of the Avatar.

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:48.850
Xai Bau grove in the spirit world is the place
where Korra confronted Zaheer.

00:01:48.850 --> 00:01:51.710
So I’m guessing the grove was a place where
Xai Bau would communicate with his fellow

00:01:51.710 --> 00:01:58.859
red lotus members or meditate by himself and
Zaheer just continued the tradition.

00:01:58.859 --> 00:02:03.170
Using the spirit realm to skype each other
is pretty badass.

00:02:03.170 --> 00:02:06.799
Eventually, Team Zaheer and Unalaq are brought
in to the order.

00:02:06.799 --> 00:02:08.710
Probably around the time they were Korra’s
age.

00:02:08.710 --> 00:02:14.190
