with her when she was a little girl.

00:02:22.510 --> 00:02:24.420
That’s just dark, even for Legend of Korra.

00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:29.200
It seems like Korra and Kuvira aren’t too
far apart in age, so it’s possible that

00:02:29.200 --> 00:02:33.750
